OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fwith evening sunny spells and then
OL,7,Fclear spells overnight. Perhaps some
OL,8,Fthicker cloud with the odd spot of
OL,9,Frain in northern coastal areas.
OL,10,FTurning a little breezy, but mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunny spells for most, but
OL,13,Fisolated showers are possible. Breezy,
OL,14,Fand cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
